- MyCHIPs legacy
  - Taleus will implement part of the next generation MyCHIPs protocol.
  - The MyCHIPs project can be found in a parallel folder to Taleus.
  - Refer to ../mychips/doc/*.md to fully understand the legacy implementation while working on this extension.

- General:
  - Use typescript
  - Handle functions like cryptography, conversions centrally, consistently
  - Use test-driven workflow as much as possible

- Project Phases
  - Design
  - Documentation
  - TLA+ modeling if appropriate
  - Testing, coding
  - Integration
    - Integrate back into MyCHIPs engine
    - Standalone mobile phone implementation
  - Maintenance
